posting_body: ["That's right, you CAN have it all!", 'We are ready to do all we can to help you with your home search.', 'Please call or email us today to see how you can schedule a virtual or in-person tour.', 'Going on NOW!', '- Waived application fee', '- $250 off first month', '_______________________________________', 'Koz at the Dome is bringing affordable, state-of-the-art housing to anyone in Tacoma, WA who meet rental criteria.', 'Our brand new, lux studios will be the perfect home to meet your needs.', 'Located in Tacoma, your home at Koz at the Dome is mere steps away from the Tacoma Dome as well as a variety of shopping, dining, and transportation options.', 'Contact us today to learn more about the exciting features Koz at the Dome has to offer.', 'Call or email for availability!', '• Free Utilities included with rent*', '• Free Wi-Fi assigned personal secured password*', '• Pet Friendly', '• Brand new features', '• Spacious Ceilings', '• Ceiling fans', '• Bike Storage', '• Washer/Dryer conveniently located on site', '• Secured Entrance', '• Outdoor Courtyard', '*Additional occupant $45.00 monthly rate', '*Income restricted units available']
